<input type="hidden" value="<%= params[:category] %>" id="sun_category" />
<div class="payment" id="payment_sun" style="display: none">
  <span class="close" id="close_sun">关闭</span>
  <div class="pay_title">1）已经兑换的小太阳不能完全使用可以联系客户退款。<br/>
    2）如在充值过程中遇到故障，请及时咨询在线客服。</div>
  <div class="pay_box">
    <h1 class="pay_way_sun">开通方式一：</h1>
    <div class="pay_con_two">
      <div class="pcon_bg"><img src="/assets/paySun_bg.jpg" /></div>
      <input name=""  id="sun_fee"  class="paySun_input" />
       <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="pay_a_tow" id="sunpay_a_tow" target="_blank" onclick="sun_charge()"></a>
    </div>
    <span class="orange">温馨提示：支付宝充值免手续费</span>
    <a href="#" class="huode_sun">如何获得更多小太阳</a>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="tab" id="tab_sun" style="display: none;">
  <span class="close" id="tab_close">关闭</span>
  <p>小太阳充值</p>
  <div class="btn_center_double"><a class="b_btn" onclick="window.open('/logins/alipay_sun?category='+<%= params[:category] %>+'&total_fee='+$('#sun_fee').val(),'_blank','height=750,width=1000,left=200,top=50');">重新支付</a><button class="b_btn" onclick="window.location.reload()">完成充值</button></div>
</div>
